abstract: NHL Roundup; New Jersey Devils beat Carolina Hurricanes, 3-2; other ice hockey scores noted.
lead_paragraph: David Schlemko’s tiebreaking goal gave the Devils a 3-2 victory on Tuesday night over the Carolina Hurricanes in Newark.
